          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="email-content">
          <h1 class="content-title">Welcome to Fifty Firsts Wellness</h1>

          <p class="greeting">Hi <%= firstName || 'there' %>,</p>

          <p class="content-text">
            We're excited to welcome you to Fifty Firsts Wellness and we're even more excited about what we've got planned. You're already on your way to creating a beautiful wellness journey.
          </p>

          <p class="content-text">
            Whether you're here for your personal growth, for your business, or just for fun — welcome! If there's anything you need, we'll be here every step of the way.
          </p>

          <div class="feature-list">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-text">
                <strong>Mindset Coaching:</strong> Develop resilience and positive thinking patterns
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-text">
                <strong>Lifestyle Wellness:</strong> Practical tools for physical and mental well-being
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-text">
                <strong>Personal Growth:</strong> Resources for continuous learning and development
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>" class="btn">Let's Get Started</a>
          </div>

          <p class="content-text" style="margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 0;">
            Thanks,<br>
            Fifty Firsts Wellness Team
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
          <div class="footer-text">
            Questions or FAQ? Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@fiftyfirstswellness.co.uk" class="footer-link">info@fiftyfirstswellness.co.uk</a>
          </div>

          <div class="footer-copyright">
            © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Fifty Firsts Wellness. All rights reserved.
          </div>
